Contribute
==========

The Elveos.org website is an open source project and we are open to any kind of help.

You could:

 * Report a bug, suggest a feature, report a translation error using the report bug form in the side bar.
 * Update or create a new translation from the [po files](https://gitorious.org/bloatit/bloatit/trees/master/main/po)
 * Send a patch
 * ...
 
The public work repository can be found on gitorious: [elveos repository](https://gitorious.org/bloatit)
